column5: went out fishing a couple place yesterday and today along the rec canal in welland yesterday went out for three hours befor dark and got a few crappie and a couple gills  and today we went to the same place my girlfriend got the only crappie today and we got some more perch and gills my father will post pics
Nice feed of panies Rob D Did Bruce tag along with you guys??  Your fathers welcome gift was put in the mail this AM.  You can expect it end of next week Thanks for sharing Jacques
